---
title: Double Katsu Pork & Broccoli Egg Noodles with Corianer & Crushed Peanuts
description: You’ll be off to visit your happy place when you get a taste of this dish. Pork mince is tossed in katsu paste and mellowed out with coconut milk to create a perfectly balanced dish, with egg noodles to help slurp up all that sauce!
We’ve replaced the green beans in this recipe with baby broccoli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just
follow your recipe card!
